Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco/Oakland Bay Bridge
A restaurant, a 24-hour fitness center, and a bar/lounge are available at this smoke-free hotel. WiFi in public areas is free. Other amenities include a spa tub, a business center, and conference space.  All 278 rooms provide free WiFi and free wired Internet, LCD TVs with cable channels, and conveniences like refrigerators and microwaves. Guests will also find MP3 docks, room service, and coffee makers. 

Emeryville
Located in Emeryville, Hilton Garden Inn San Francisco/Oakland Bay Bridge is in the business district and near the bay. Berkeley Marina and Ferry Building are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area&#x27;s popular attractions can visit University of California Botanical Garden at Berkeley and Aquarium of the Bay. Looking to enjoy an event or a game? See what&#x27;s going on at Oracle Park, or consider The Regency Ballroom for a night out. Our guests appreciate the hotel&#x27;s central and quiet location. 
